There are different types of background checks that can be run. Let's review below!

Pre-Employment

This BGC will screen applicants quickly and thoroughly to get them hired.


Hide
Post-Hire

This BGC will allow clients to be proactive rather than reactive. This type of screen allows the client to learn about criminal activity and risky red flags that can occur when someone is working for you, through Foley's monitor and rescreening services.


Hide
Verifications

This type of BGC ensures the educational and professional history on an applicant's resumes are correct. This includes education verification, employment verification, professional reference interview, and professional license verifications.


Hide
Drug & Health

This BGC will keep your organization safe by conducting pre-employment drug and medical tests.


Hide
Criminal

This BGC screens for criminal history thorough county, statewide, and federal searches.


Hide
Social Media

This BGC will scour an applicant's online activity for behaviors that could put your company at risk.


